actionConfiguration.body:
SELECT OID,CUSTOMER_APPLICANT_EMAIL,CUSTOMER_PARTICIPANT_TYPE,CUSTOMER_APPLICANT_NAME,CUSTOMER_APPLICANT_MOBILE,CUSTOMER_COUNTRY_CODE,CUSTOMER_BUSINESS_GSTN_DESC,CUSTOMER_BUSINESS_CONST_TYPE FROM aps_customer  where CUSTOMER_APPLICANT_MOBILE= {{vayApplicantMobile.text}} and 	CUSTOMER_APPLICANT_EMAIL = {{vayApplicantEmail.text}} and CUSTOMER_PARTICIPANT_TYPE = {{vayRoleSelection.selectedOptionValue}} and CUSTOMER_COUNTRY_CODE = {{vayCountryofRegistration.selectedOptionValue}} and CUSTOMER_BUSINESS_GSTN_DESC = {{vayTINGSTIN.text}}
 ;
